targets.query: SELECT "active" FROM "gatling2_users" WHERE "scenario" = 'allUsers'  AND "simulation" =~ /^$simulation$/ AND $timeFilter GROUP BY "request"
SELECT "count"  / 10 FROM "gatling2" WHERE ("request" = 'allRequests' AND "status" = 'ok' AND "simulation" =~ /^$simulation$/) AND $timeFilter
SELECT "count" FROM "gatling2" WHERE ("request" = 'allRequests' AND "status" = 'ko' AND "simulation" =~ /^$simulation$/) AND $timeFilter
SELECT "count"  / 10 FROM "gatling2" WHERE ("request" = 'allRequests' AND "status" = 'ok' AND "simulation" =~ /^$simulation$/) AND $timeFilter
SELECT "count" FROM "gatling2" WHERE "request" != 'allRequests' AND "status" = 'ok' AND "simulation" =~ /^$simulation$/ AND $timeFilter GROUP BY "request"
SELECT "count" / 10 FROM "gatling2" WHERE "request" != 'allRequests' AND "status" = 'ko' AND "simulation" =~ /^$simulation$/ AND $timeFilter GROUP BY "request"
SELECT mean("percentiles99") FROM "gatling2" WHERE "request" != 'allRequests' AND "simulation" =~ /^$simulation$/ AND "status" = 'ok' AND $timeFilter GROUP BY "request"
SELECT mean("percentiles99") FROM "gatling2" WHERE "request" != 'allRequests' AND "simulation" =~ /^$simulation$/ AND "status" = 'ok' AND $timeFilter GROUP BY "request"
SELECT "percentiles50" FROM "gatling2" WHERE "request" != 'allRequests' AND "simulation" =~ /^$simulation$/ AND "status" = 'ok' AND $timeFilter GROUP BY "request"
SELECT "percentiles95" FROM "gatling2" WHERE "request" != 'allRequests' AND "simulation" =~ /^$simulation$/ AND "status" = 'ok' AND $timeFilter GROUP BY "request"
SELECT "percentiles99" FROM "gatling2" WHERE "request" != 'allRequests' AND "simulation" =~ /^$simulation$/ AND "status" = 'ok' AND $timeFilter GROUP BY "request"
SELECT "mean" FROM "gatling2" WHERE "request" != 'allRequests' AND "simulation" =~ /^$simulation$/ AND "status" = 'ok' AND $timeFilter GROUP BY "request"
SELECT "max" FROM "gatling2" WHERE "request" != 'allRequests' AND "simulation" =~ /^$simulation$/ AND "status" = 'ok' AND $timeFilter GROUP BY "request"
SELECT "max" FROM "gatling2" WHERE "request" != 'allRequests' AND "simulation" =~ /^$simulation$/ AND "status" = 'ok' AND $timeFilter GROUP BY "request"

list.name: system_under_test
list.query: show tag values  from gatling2 with key="system_under_test"

list.name: test_environment
list.query: show tag values from gatling2 with key="test_environment" where "system_under_test" =~ /$system_under_test/

list.name: simulation
list.query: SHOW TAG VALUES from gatling2 WITH KEY = "simulation" where "system_under_test" =~ /$system_under_test/ and "test_environment" =~ /$test_environment/

templatingVariables.name: system_under_test
templatingVariables.query: show tag values  from gatling2 with key="system_under_test"

templatingVariables.name: test_environment
templatingVariables.query: show tag values from gatling2 with key="test_environment" where "system_under_test" =~ /.*/

templatingVariables.name: simulation
templatingVariables.query: SHOW TAG VALUES from gatling2 WITH KEY = "simulation" where "system_under_test" =~ /.*/ and "test_environment" =~ /.*/
